
docker-compose up -d
http://localhost:80    // vai aparecer a página do template bootstrap
docker-compose up -d --build  // Build images before starting containers.
docker-compose down
docker image ls // vai ter o nginx 1.13 que foi usado no nginx.Dockerfile
docker-compose down --help

docker-compose down --help
docker-compose down --rmi local // 'local': Remove only images that don't have a custom tag set by the `image` field.


----- Anotações -----

docker-compose up --build
Vai usar o arquivo nginx.Dockerfile, está declarado
no atributo "build" do docker-compose.yml.


docker-compose down --rmi local
--rmi type              Remove images. Type must be one of:
                          'all': Remove all images used by any service.
                          'local': Remove only images that don't have a
                          custom tag set by the `image` field.
